Visualization Problem 5

Colaberry just started a class of 130+ students.  It is more important than ever
that we have a way to monitor incoming tickets to see if they are being
handled in a timely manner.

Currently The First Contact Resolution rate is 4.31%, which 86.94% lower than
its target(33%) and The Average First Respond hours is 36.08hrs on weekends
which is 50.35% lower than the goal(24hrs). The insight provides a better
approach why the performance of customer service agents is declining and how
to resolve the problem.
